#. Id: 55049-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Garret bar patrons
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: IS_LEADER=1, Tag: -1
#: 55049-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Drink up slave, I ain't made of sake..."
msgstr "喝了奴隸，我不是用清酒製成的......"

#. Id: 55046-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (55048-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Extra 1 (2)
#. -- Group title: Garret bar patrons
#: 55046-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... So... why have you bought a slave into the bar, Garret? "
msgstr "......那麼......為什麼你在酒吧買了一個奴隸，加勒特？"

#. Id: 55050-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (55046-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Garret bar patrons
#: 55050-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Treatin' 'im to a drink, he's worked hard this week. And a happy slave makes a good slave... See? Look at his 'lil face, he's lovin' it."
msgstr "我想喝酒，他本週努力工作。而一個幸福的奴隸會成為一個好奴隸......看到了嗎？看看他的'lil face，他很喜歡它。"

#. Id: 55051-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55050-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Extra 1 (2)
#. -- Group title: Garret bar patrons
#: 55051-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Goddammit, Garret, a bar ain't for slaves. Feed 'em sake and they ain't gonna respect you. You gotta keep 'em on their toes, give 'em a few lashings, not sakes... Seems like slave-lover words if you ask me..."
msgstr "Goddammit，Garret，酒吧不適合奴隸。餵他們的緣故，他們不會尊重你。你得保持他們的腳趾，給他們一些鞭子，而不是噓聲...如果你問我，似乎像奴隸愛人的話......"

#. Id: 55054-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (55053-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Extra 2 (3)
#. -- Group title: Garret bar patrons
#: 55054-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "*Smash* Slave-lover?! Who said slave-lover?!"
msgstr "* Smash * Slave-lover ?!誰說奴隸愛人？！"

#. Id: 55055-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55054-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Garret bar patrons
#: 55055-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Shhh! Keep your voice down, would you? I ain't no slave lover. This un's just havin' a drink while he carries my baggage, that's all... Take it easy."
msgstr "噓！保持低調，是嗎？我不是沒有奴隸的情人。這個聯合國祇是在他搬運我的行李時喝酒，這就是全部......放輕鬆。"
